
Pod::Compiler
-------------

This is an evaluation distribution of a POD compiler that turns
POD documents into an object tree that can be conveniently
processed by any backends.

Main areas of application are converters to complex output formats
like HTML, LaTeX or FrameMaker.

Example applications are included:
podlint is a tool to beautify existing POD documentation and to
please podchecker.

CONTENTS

This package contains

Pod::Compiler - the workhorse module
Pod::node - a package for POD hyperlink nodes/destinations
podchecker2 - a script that checks syntax of POD documents
podlint - a script that beautifies existing POD documents

AUTHOR

Marek Rouchal, reusing (huge) parts of many existing POD converters.

